itu-mcs1.def: Indicators in this group deal with all fixed Internet subscriptions, whether broadband or narrowband. The next section (fixed broadband subscriptions) deals with broadband connections. The distinction between narrowband and broadband is the download speed of the fixed connection: in order to be categorized as broadband it must offer a speed of at least 256 kbit/s
itu-mcs1.name: Mobile-cellular subscriptions per 100 inhabitants
itu-mcs1.source: ITU, Wor​ld Telecommun​ic​ation/ICT Indicators Database​​, August 2042
